SONATA,Sedan,@XWXW-lk4jf,"Straight to the Toyota dealer is not an option is you are seeking performance on a budget.  Yes, Toyota has been recently taking a page out of Hyundai and Kia's book in that they have started to introduce powerful new vehicles.  That said, most of those are expensive SUV's or vehicles like the Crown or GR Corolla, both of which are much more expensive with similar or less performance.  They no longer make the V6 Camry and when they did, it was a slower vehicle.  The options for the Camey that they have now are not enthusiast focused.  They are now designed to be efficient appliances which are great for many, but not for those seeking a bit more.",1,SONATA,0
