IONIQ 6,Sedan,@atomiconnection,"I just bought this vehicle. I totally fell in with this car the moment I saw it in person. It gave me the feel of Audi A7. I would take Ionic 6 over 5, hands down, because the sporty design of 6 provides a compelling presence. I think, for the general public, they may confuse it with a Porsche or a Tesla. It’s a futuristic comparison without the knock off feel. I’m sure I will feel fine with that",28,IONIQ 6,4
