IONIQ 6,Sedan,@yandbmakeg,"Have had the 6 for almost a week. Nice so far. I would say those range numbers are on the low end. Been seeing numbers well into the 300s myself and from others with the AWD drive SEL and Limited models, and as stated by others the SE RWD gets 360 miles of range. Though I am driving exclusively in ECO mode and use the I-Pedal as much as possible. Also an interesting note, those wings on the sides of the dash are screens for side cameras (replacing the side mirrors), which are unfortunately not allowed in the US. Wish they had found a use for the screens on the US models.",26,IONIQ 6,0
