AVANTE,Sedan,@psuntlion,"I just came across this video again as I’m getting ready to pull the trigger on an Elantra N as an unexpected and somewhat surprising replacement to my ‘23 M3 that I sold last month.  Like Thomas said, I’m completely torn as to whether to buy the manual or the DCT.  I drove both the other day, and the manual had me lol’ing at its eagerness and all of the popping and banging off throttle.  The DCT is quicker on paper and would definitely be easier to live with as a daily, but it didn’t feel like nearly as much of a hooligan as the manual.  Tough decision!

