TUCSON,SUV,@Oo-IIII-oO,"The plastic coolant pipe out of the reservoir is copied from the german manufacturers. They have been using the exact same (lousy) design for years. (especially VW Audi but I see it on BMW and Mercedes a lot) Same goes for the hood latch cable. The reason for that is they assmble the complete front end radiator support as a package off the car,  then bolt it on and plug in the wire harness and the hood release cable. It was NOT designed for easy service. It just happened to look like it is.",5,TUCSON,0
