TUCSON,SUV,@Ricky-mo6mv,"I lease a 2023 Tucson Limited ICE and I absolutely love it. At this point, I plan on buying out my lease as I really don’t want to part with it or drive anything else. The ergonomics, visibility, comfort, and quality of materials are outstanding. Mine of course is pre-refresh, but I actually like not having any knobs as it’s so easy to clean. I also find it to have a more unique interior design than the refresh. 

In terms of the exterior appearance, it seems people either love it or hate it. But we always have to give Hyundai and KIA credit for making big design statements that ultimately set trends. I have a few design degrees, and I see the Tucson as a work of art that is very pleasing to my eye. There certainly are a ton of thes on the road, so Hyundai is certainly doing more than a few things right.",6,TUCSON,4
