TUCSON,SUV,@jeffallen8150,"I get the love of simple access to the air filter for change.  But if the design does not seal properly around the filter element, it will allow dirt to bypass the filter.  Briggs and Stratton had a similar issue when they went with a quick access design for their lawn tractor engines.  
Can you comment further on how well the Hyundai design seals around the filter element?  It seems like it slid out a little too easy.
