TUCSON,SUV,@ronpashley-crawford8375,Great review.  I live in Scotland and my wife bought a  2022 Tucson Hybrid Ultimate 3 months ago.  Now I'm one of these weirdos that change my own oil and filter regularly.  Why do Hyundai have different cartridge oil filter housings for different models instead of spin-on filters?  The one on the hybrid has a locking pin that slots through the housing and into the filter cartridge rim.  There's too many parts that can go wrong and create a leak.,0,TUCSON,0
