INSTER,SUV,@MaskedMammal,"Hey, maybe if I keep saying BRING THIS TO THE USA it will eventually manifest into Hyundai taking a chance on a completely untapped market here.

This is exactly the perfect sized car for me. Fits 4 comfortably in a super flexible space, spacious in all the ways I could want it to without a massive footprint on the road. It looks tiny and fun, but inside you don't feel like it's tiny. There's maybe ONE other EV in our whole country that's this size, and it (the Fiat 500e) is too expensive and looks truly cramped inside. This is exactly the kind of entry-level EV that I could see actually changing people's minds about compact cars here.",0,INSTER,0
