INSTER,SUV,@csjrogerson2377,"It suits the main aim of EVs as a commuting, shopping trolley, school runner but its far too expensive.  You can get much better, more practical ICE cars at several thousand pounds less. The battery capacity and range figures do not compute. 4.3 m/kw at 42kwh is 180 miles, not 203, nor is 49 kwh at 4.2 m/kw 229 miles, its 206!!!!  Then adjust according to whose figures WLTP etc. In addition the battery is NMC, so the 80/10 rule applies.  Thus regular range is 126 miles & 144 miles.  Not paying 23-30 grand for that.",0,INSTER,0
